Matthew 24 : 
14 And this gospel of the kingdom shall be preached in all the world [οἰκουμένῃ - oikoumenē] for a witness unto all nations; and then shall the end come.
Luke 2 :1 
And it came to pass in those days, that there went out a decree from Caesar Augustus, that all the world [οἰκουμένην - oikoumenēn] should be taxed
